sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant Lambda as Neptune Lambda
    participant Neptune as Amazon Neptune
    participant DDB as DynamoDB (AuditTrail)
    participant CW as CloudWatch Logs
    
    User->>Frontend: Calculate trust score
    Frontend->>APIGW: POST /neptune/score
    APIGW->>Lambda: Invoke with payload
    
    Note over Lambda: Build Gremlin query
    
    Lambda->>Neptune: Execute Gremlin Query
    
    Note over Neptune: Graph traversal - 2-hop connection found
    
    Neptune-->>Lambda: Return paths (50-100ms)
    
    Note over Lambda: Calculate trust score
    
    Lambda->>DDB: PutItem - Log scoring
    DDB-->>Lambda: Success
    
    Lambda->>CW: Log query metrics
    
    Lambda-->>APIGW: Return trust score
    APIGW-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: Display graph visualization
    
    Note over User,CW: Total latency: 50-150ms
